Using the NETCONF Configuration Protocol
over Secure SHell (SSH)
2006", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC4742.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document describes a method for invoking and running the Network Configuration Protocol (NETCONF) within a Secure Shell (SSH) session as an SSH subsystem. [STANDARDS-TRACK]"];
